{"tid":728763,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好僧自己住個區好想走","createTime":"2018-07-04T03:59:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T08:29:39.000Z","uid":12386,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4a4a79fa947e7f6fdb1c36626809fe48e0ebb516","tid":728763,"uid":12386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T03:59:31.000Z","msg":"愈黎愈覺得自己住個區有問題<br />\n香港土生土長,細個住元朗,小學三年班開始住天水圍<br />\n可能細個個陣,未建立價值觀,覺得住個區都冇咩問題<br />\n到依家廿中,可能社會轉變等等因素,依家覺得天水圍真係會住到人痴撚線<br />\n<br />\n講食野,街市/超級市場係會<br />\n1. 食物變壞仲放出黎賣<br />\n2. 食物全部比班C9揀到爛哂<br />\n3. 食物性價物極貴,比正價買垃圾<br />\n<br />\n講居住<br />\n1. 地點離返工好遠,區內冇就業(咁呢樣都可以理解)<br />\n2. 衛生極差,居民覺得自己做緊既野係冇問題<br />\n3. 夜晚好撚嘈,久唔久就會某單位有人大大聲鬧交,樓下有班MK係到嘈,一班男人/阿叔係到飲酒大大聲傾計,完全訓唔到覺,有時訓訓下都嘈醒"},{"pid":"fac217e7190272cce1601281fa68b0d3bee7fa16","tid":728763,"uid":12386,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:02:06.000Z","msg":"仲有就係d餐廳（包括連鎖店）都係會將變壞左既食物拎出黎賣<br />\n<br />\n到都係餐廳班廚覺得無問題定係買個班人覺得無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"126710413038cd5f28304825bb3de987b2e15b0c","tid":728763,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:41:41.000Z","msg":"仲有大部分小學生同佢地老母都講蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c730b28bd695f8bd5d851d36229d64a2c3bd16","tid":728763,"uid":86651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:48:11.000Z","msg":"又多南亞狗 蝗學生 廢老 貪小便宜師奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"642d11dc0cdf91fdaec4228221738d08c91150fa","tid":728763,"uid":85564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:26:46.000Z","msg":"深水埗，天水圍<br />\n<br />\n堪稱香港雙水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55ca8db91f5b7fc873c416daa0bd792d881d5271","tid":728763,"uid":62326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:30:00.000Z","msg":"搭車又唔比人落車先 係咁逼<br />\n西鐵搭電梯又唔排隊係執邊sip入黎 好黑人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2b7e56a4f11f7078172ccf2f83cf5b9bcb2f3f","tid":728763,"uid":192722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T06:19:08.000Z","msg":"天水圍得新北冮算係有野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d538c337ba4229e0cd8e4850b06557a405db4b57","tid":728763,"uid":84432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T06:50:32.000Z","msg":"成個天水圍都死氣沉沉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44afc35ad89f1f74e8b8ecf68b11d700355a2a5f","tid":728763,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T06:56:46.000Z","msg":"以前住間細舊屋周圍都係香港人講廣東話，之後搬左去其他區間新屋先發覺周圍變左都係蝗國人同腩亞賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5481e86b37a260280116977813a97fcee6b6798a","tid":728763,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T07:07:23.000Z","msg":"我同樓主好似<br />\n細個元朗<br />\n中二搬去天水圍<br />\n<br />\n前排搬左去秀茂坪（理論上係觀塘喎）<br />\n而家好掛住元朗<br />\n好想返去撚貓同食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14fd528940ae1c3fc8fe8ff82ed164f3c2bd56f1","tid":728763,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44afc35ad89f1f74e8b8ecf68b11d700355a2a5f","tid":728763,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T06:56:46.000Z","msg":"以前住間細舊屋周圍都係香港人講廣東話，之後搬左去其他區間新屋先發覺周圍變左都係蝗國人同腩亞賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T07:07:55.000Z","msg":"新屋邨好撚多大陸人痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":